  <article itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/UserComments" id="comment-2090554" class="single-comment">
    <div>
      <header>        <div>
                      <a href="/users/Suchindranath/comments" title="View Suchindranath&#039;s profile">Suchindranath</a>                                <time itemprop="dateCreated" dateTime="2013-07-17T05:13:00+0000" class="created" title="2013-07-17T05:13:34+00:00">Jul 17th 2013 5:13 GMT</time>
        </div>
      </header>
      <div class="comment-body"><p>The UN is run by a bureaucracy that enjoys even more impunity and incompetence that that of India or Stalinist Russia. Does anybody remember that the UN introduced the "Nile Perch" into Lake Victoria with devastating effect? The Tilapia used to be fished from dug outs, sun-baked and eaten by the natives. The Nile Perch did away with the Tilapia, de-forested the environment as it needed fire wood to be cooked. It did away with the livelihood of the local fishermen and the non-Wild Life protein intake of East-Central Africa. Asian Factory Ship Owners and European Fish consumers were the real beneficiaries.</p>
</div>
      <footer class="clearfix">
                  <ul class="links"><li class="comment_recommend first"><a href="/vote/recommend-comment/2090554?nid=21581878&amp;page=0&amp;sort=0&amp;token=3847ad98ff6d19051a5b510aacacbb75" title="Recommend comment: The UN is run by a" class="recommend" data-ec-omniture="recommend_comment" rel="nofollow">Recommend</a> <div><span>32</span></div></li>
