      <header>        <div>
                      <a href="/users/TS2912/comments" title="View TS2912&#039;s profile">TS2912</a>                                <time itemprop="dateCreated" dateTime="2013-07-17T04:02:00+0000" class="created" title="2013-07-17T04:02:28+00:00">Jul 17th 2013 4:02 GMT</time>
        </div>
      </header>
      <div class="comment-body"><p>#1 - Is it the UN's fault for (unwittingly) bringing in a Cholera infection?</p>
<p>#2 - Or Haiti's fault for not having a sewage system (which would make such diseases a non-issue)?</p>
<p>If is is #1, then I could sue my neighbor for giving me a cold,<br />
- which turned into pneumonia<br />
- because I did not have health insurance to visit my primary care physician<br />
- causing my condition to become life-threatening</p>
</div>
