      <div class="comment-body"><p>The United Nations costs billions of dollars per year. Does it prevent wars? No. Does it provide basic sanitation for countries in disaster zones? No. Does it provide any semblance of social justice or quality of life for millions of oppressed women, children and minority populations worldwide? Hell no. </p>
<p>Does it hold conferences and wank on forever about the evils of climate change and copyright violation? Yes.</p>
